rComments: Very nice professor, her lecturing style is kind of disjointedall over the place (which seems to be common among practitioner professors) but she keeps the class engaged.
Great professor! Really cares about her students and is passionate both about her practice and about teaching!

Great professor.  Very empathetic, cares about her student, great discussion facilitator.  Explains concepts crystal clear.  Brings her practice experience into the classroom.  She can be a bit scattered re: readings, timelines and schedules, which is very frustrating.  Overall, great professor.
